    "description": "<br><br>（存在しない）Ziggyの靴に準備をしてください - スウェーデンの架空の近隣地域からの予想外のヒーロー。一緒に、あなたは潜在的に世界全体を壊滅させる可能性のある陰険な計画を阻止する大変な課題に取り組むことになります。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/9dd9804afa88caa3e470188adf848b15.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br><br>Ziggy有一天醒来，手上有一个奇怪的印记，对前一天晚上发生的事情毫无头绪。在他熟悉的郊区街道中迷失了几分钟后，一场爆炸将他带回到他之前醒来的地方……他被困在一个时间循环中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/6860594574c18939d00da88aa6cee33b.poster.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/6860594574c18939d00da88aa6cee33b.webm?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/6860594574c18939d00da88aa6cee33b.mp4?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/0e6e3b0665725a04adeb4f6cf0e4a963.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br><br>他没有鞋子，也没有过去的记忆，他开始了一项任务，探寻究竟发生了什么，以及如何避免他的城市受到毁灭。然而，这并不容易，因为他越是在错误的地方窥探，他就越是了解到他的故乡隐藏着许多秘密。他奇怪的邻居变得更加怪异，他只能依靠他的朋友和他高度可靠的大脑。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/a0fb73503acb94d1ed54f63dc584aa52.poster.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/a0fb73503acb94d1ed54f63dc584aa52.webm?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/a0fb73503acb94d1ed54f63dc584aa52.mp4?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/68a901405945d6332d9660fcd7c1335c.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br><br>如果一天又一天地重复，那么该如何前进呢？这就是问题所在：在奥尔滕，知识是你前进的关键。每个你经历的循环，你都会学到一些新的东西，这将让你推动故事的发展。有了这个时间循环机制，你将保留线索、笔记和时间线事件，最终了解如何在一个轻松的星期天中改变未来，仅需12分钟。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/e138a95958bdf289e9d3c6460d61570d.poster.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/e138a95958bdf289e9d3c6460d61570d.webm?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/e138a95958bdf289e9d3c6460d61570d.mp4?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/0cd162be039fd9485849f4bb6fccdf1b.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=86 /></span><br><br>他们是谁？午夜委员会，我的意思是。他们似乎是唯一一个比你领先一步的人。这个城镇40年前到底发生了什么，你如何逃脱时间循环和死亡？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/4f19e543ab257a802256d925d80d8cb5.poster.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/4f19e543ab257a802256d925d80d8cb5.webm?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/4f19e543ab257a802256d925d80d8cb5.mp4?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> 跟随线索，解决谜题，探索奥尔滕这个神秘的郊区，在这款2.5D手绘冒险游戏中探险！ </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/19cce7219f407a2055add6fb34fe8853.poster.avif?t=1709067727\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/19cce7219f407a2055add6fb34fe8853.webm?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785420/extras/19cce7219f407a2055add6fb34fe8853.mp4?t=1709067727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
